title: Jesse James' Women 1954 (Classic Cowboy Western) by Don 'Red' Barry

sources.title: Jesse James' Women 1954 (Classic Cowboy Western) by Don 'Red' Barry
sources.description:
HIS DEADLY EXPLOITS, ADVENTURES ROARING WITH EXCITEMENT!...And the Women Who Made the West Wonderful, Wild and Deadly!  
Jesse James keeps so busy skirt-chasing that his outlaw career starts to suffer.
 
Original title: Jesse James' Women (1954)

Director: Don 'Red' Barry
Writers: D.D. Beauchamp, William R. Cox, Don 'Red' Berry 
Stars: Don 'Red' Barry, Peggie Castle, Jack Buetel, Lita Baron
Genres: Classics, Western
